HEADWORD: Necktie
<hw>Neck"tie`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A scarf, band, or
kerchief of silk, etc., passing around the neck or collar and tied in
front; a bow of silk, etc., fastened in front of the neck.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

